DEITZWEISSMAN M&C:"The Shopper Friendly Savings Discount Store"
Mission : "Making Shopping More Affordable Each and Everyday"

Who We are


Congratulations and thank you for taking time to stop by our website to learn about our company and what it is that we do.


Our company name is DEITZWEISSMAN Marketing & Consulting; however, we are commonly recognized as DEITZWEISSMAN M&C.


DEITZWEISSMAN M&C is an independent and privately owned e-commerce retail store. Our company was established in July of 2014 and has been in operation since then.


Here at DEITZWEISSMAN M&C we focus on one thing and that is consumer retail cost savings. Our company sells low cost brand name and private label products to the public. Our business specifically focuses on the sale of low cost consumer nonperishable grocery products and household items to the public.


We serve to function and do in fact function as a recognized authentic e-commerce discount store because our prices always remain low. Our e-commerce store also offers some the best convenience in shopping to consumers making purchases from our store because we are committed to our goals and consistent in the services that we provide.




Purpose


We serve to function and do in fact function as a recognized authentic e-commerce discount store because our prices always remain low. Our e-commerce store also offers some the best convenience in shopping to consumers making purchases from our store because we are committed to our goals and consistent in the services that we provide.


Our for-profit organization is also interested in combating poverty and hunger in the United States. Through our store, we provide many


purchasing opportunities for families or individuals less fortunate so they can obtain needed and necessary food items and household goods. Our e-commerce store enables our organization to operate and maintain our commitment of helping eliminate the problem of poverty and hunger in the United States through the services our organization provides on a regular basis.


At DEITZWEISSMAN M&C, we believe we have been afforded the opportunity to successfully reach a larger cross-section of the population with cost savings on desired or necessary grocery products and household items that can and will benefit all.


As we grow, we will continue to pursue opportunities that will make it more affordable for all of our customers to shop and purchase low cost consumer nonperishable food and household products on an on going basis.
